    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in exceptional, mint condition and presents as if it were brand new. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, factory-fresh luster with absolutely no scratches, dings, or paint chips. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the upholstery, dashboard, and carpets show no signs of use, and every electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open checkbook. Buyers can expect a vehicle that is collector-grade and requires nothing but a new owner to appreciate its perfect state.",
      "price": 49500.0,
